The paper focuses on obstacle detection for self-driving cars using a combination of deep learning and geometric modeling. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category, as it deals with detecting potential hazards on the road.
